      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">42.1107</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2530e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2556e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.242-2.dita#FAR_52_242_2"
                        base="i1048000"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.242-2</xref>, Production Progress Reports, in solicitations and contracts when production progress reporting is required; unless a construction contract, or a Federal Supply Schedule contract is contemplated.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2556e18">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            When the clause at <xref href="52.242-2.dita#FAR_52_242_2"
                        base="i1048000"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.242-2</xref> is used, the contracting officer shall specify appropriate reporting instructions in the Schedule (see <xref href="42.1106.dita#FAR_42_1106"
                        base="i1074878"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42.1106</xref>(a)).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
